name: Symmetric
description: Symmetric is a Decentralised Exchange (DEX) and an Automated Market Maker (AMM) on Celo and Gnosis chain. Symmetric version 2 supports multi-asset pools (for diversifying exposure), Liquidity Bootstrapping Pools (LBPs) for launching new tokens and customisable pools for more specific use-cases (such as thematic investing, indexes & ETFs).
